BAR Lobby is a new WIP lobby for the RTS game Beyond All Reason.
It hopes to boldly go where no Spring client has gone before,
providing a more streamlined experience, with good visuals and UX
being high priority. The ultimate goal of BAR Lobby is to replace
all other lobbies when it comes to playing BAR. If a significant
amount of people don't wish to use it because of reasons such as
functionality or speed, then this project is going very wrong.
